            "detailed_description": "Vindictive Drive is a Thriller/Action game with cyberpunk elements and Real Time Action/Stealth mechanics following Arris Fern, a young woman in her cold blooded revenge against her father, the president of the most powerful nation, for the assassination of her mother 12 years ago.<br>Completely consumed by hatred and resentment, Arris will use the most cruel methods at her disposal to achieve her goal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Vindictive Drive's &quot;battle system&quot; rely on outsmarting security systems, avoiding cameras, and fooling your enemies using your computer and jamming devices, leaving the pistol as last resort.<br></li><li>Stealth is an important part of the game, you will be able to disable alarms and create distractions.<br></li><li>Story rich scenarios and suspense.<br></li><li>Talkative and friendly NPCs.<br></li><li>A lot of illustrations and animations made frame per frame.<br></li><li>Arris' very sour behavior.<br></li><li>Multiple endings.</li></ul>",
            "about_the_game": "Vindictive Drive is a Thriller/Action game with cyberpunk elements and Real Time Action/Stealth mechanics following Arris Fern, a young woman in her cold blooded revenge against her father, the president of the most powerful nation, for the assassination of her mother 12 years ago.<br>Completely consumed by hatred and resentment, Arris will use the most cruel methods at her disposal to achieve her goal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Vindictive Drive's &quot;battle system&quot; rely on outsmarting security systems, avoiding cameras, and fooling your enemies using your computer and jamming devices, leaving the pistol as last resort.<br></li><li>Stealth is an important part of the game, you will be able to disable alarms and create distractions.<br></li><li>Story rich scenarios and suspense.<br></li><li>Talkative and friendly NPCs.<br></li><li>A lot of illustrations and animations made frame per frame.<br></li><li>Arris' very sour behavior.<br></li><li>Multiple endings.</li></ul>",
            "short_description": "Vindictive Drive is an Action/Stealth game about Arris Fern's cold blooded revenge against her father, the president of the most powerful nation, for the assassination of her mother. Consumed by hatred, Arris will use the most cruel methods at her disposal to achieve her goal.",
            "supported_languages": "English, Spanish - Spain",
            "reviews": "“I would play this game again one day when the full release comes about, and I do wish the developer the best of luck; he has put the effort to make this game unique, and while I may not be the numero uno fan I do know that there is a fan base that would enjoy this type of stealth thriller indie title. Get your cyberpunk hacking terror on the go and seek your vengeance!”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://thegamerholics.com/vindictive-drive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamerholics</a><br><br>“Il team creativo che ha dato vita a Vindictive Drive è molto piccolo e perciò bisognerebbe sempre tenere conto dello sforzo compiuto in questo senso.  La storia comunque è veramente il centro di tutto e una volta che vi approccerete a questo gioco dovrete sempre tenerne conto, più che ogni altro aspetto di grafica da tripla A ad esempio.”<br>7.5 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://hotmc.com/vindictive-drive/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Hotmc™</a><br>",
